      <h3 class="title"><a target="_blank" href="http://bbs.qyer.com/thread-569570-1.html" data-bn-ipg="travelnotes-essence-5-2">圆自己个童话般的梦——12年春港澳自助7日游详细攻略游记</a></h3>

      <div>
        <p class="fr"><span class="time">2012-02-06</span><span class="bbsview" title="查看">279994</span><span class="bbsreply" title="回复">922</span><span class="bbslike" title="喜欢">68</span></p>
